## Feature richness vs 10/10 target — PASS on substance
Hero CRM (sort/filter/search/bulk/export/inline status/add-lead), drill-down modal (screenshot, audit sub-scores, DM card, contact info, notes), discovery pipeline drawer, real WebGPU panel (navigator.gpu + SmolVLM inference), 50 seeded leads, 6 live Flask endpoints with own SQLite. Every brief requirement (discovery engine, WebGPU audit, contact enrichment, CRM dashboard, persistence) is represented. Scope matches 10/10.

## BLOCKER (hard gate) — fix required
- **workSamples.js registry entry is MISSING.** Registry ends at `auction-scraper` (id 15); there is no `client-finder-1-0` object. The build report claimed registration but it was never written. This breaks DoD #3 (`/work-samples/client-finder-1-0` must return 200) and #4 (gallery card + demo link surfaced by the site). Without it the deploy ships a demo the portfolio never links to.

